        <item>
            <title>1.1.7</title>
            <description><![CDATA[<h3>Changed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Switch distribution format from zip to DMG with Applications shortcut and custom Finder layout (large icons, square window)</li>
</ul>
<h3>Fixed</h3>
<ul>
<li>Fix "Move to Applications" failing with a read-only volume error when the app is launched from a downloaded zip without moving it first (Gatekeeper App Translocation)</li>
<li>Show "Copy to Applications" dialog instead of "Move" when the app is launched from a disk image (DMG)</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
